            <fr:addr type="user">jms-0030</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>jms-0030.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Category with representable maps">Category with representable maps</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>A <fr:em>category with representable maps</fr:em> or <fr:em>CwR</fr:em> is defined by <fr:link href="uemura-2021-thesis.xml" title="Abstract and Concrete Type Theories" addr="uemura-2021-thesis" type="local">Uemura</fr:link> to be a category <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex> with finite limits equipped with a pullback-stable class <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {R}_{\mathcal {C}}\subseteq  \mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}]]></fr:tex> of <fr:link href="jms-0031.xml" title="Exponentiable arrow" addr="jms-0031" type="local">exponentiable arrows</fr:link> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
